{"prompt": "Build a user-friendly e-commerce store for a handcrafted candle maker. The design should prominently display a warm vanilla cream.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Aroma Crafts - Handcrafted Candles</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #fefefe;\n            color: #333;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #fff8dc; /* Vanilla Cream */\n            color: #8b4513; /* Saddle Brown for contrast */\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-bottom: 3px solid #d2b48c; /* Tan border */\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            font-weight: normal;\n        }\n        nav {\n            background-color: #f5f5dc; /* Beige */\n            padding: 10px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        nav a {\n            color: #8b4513;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 20px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #d2691e; /* Chocolate */\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 30px auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        .product-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));\n            gap: 20px;\n        }\n        .product-item {\n            border: 1px solid #e0d8b0; /* Light Tan border */\n            padding: 15px;\n            text-align: center;\n            background-color: #fffaf0; /* Floral White */\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            transit