der.com/250x200/f5f5dc/8b4513?text=Warm+Cinnamon\" alt=\"Warm Cinnamon Candle\">\n                    <h3>Warm Cinnamon Spice</h3>\n                    <p>Cozy notes of cinnamon and clove for a festive feel.</p>\n                    <div class=\"price\">$18.00</div>\n                    <button class=\"cta-button\">Add to Cart</button>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\" style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 40px;\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <p>Have questions or custom requests? We'd love to hear from you!</p>\n            <p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:info@aromacrafts.com\" style=\"color: #d2691e;\">info@aromacrafts.com</a></p>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Aroma Crafts. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}